title: Al-Nasr SC (Kuwait)
text: Al Nasr Sporting Club, sometimes Al Naser Sporting Club, () is a <a href="Kuwait">Kuwait</a>i professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> club, founded on 8 June 1965, and based in <a href="Al%20Farwaniyah">Ardiyah</a>. The team has participated in the <a href="Kuwait%20Premier%20League">Kuwait Premier League</a> 26 times. Al Nasr had been promoted to the Premier League three times, as champions of <a href="Kuwaiti%20Division%20One">Kuwaiti Division One</a>.
